OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782236889
OL,3,CMajor incident declared after
OL,4,Cexplosions heard and smoke plumes seen
OL,5,Cfor miles
OL,7,FA major incident has been declared as
OL,8,Femergency services deal with a large
OL,9,Ffire causing "multiple explosions" at
OL,10,Fa recycling plant in Cheshire.
OL,12,FCrews from at least 20 engines are
OL,13,Ftackling with the blaze on Everite
OL,14,FRoad in Widnes.
OL,16,FIt is thought to involve around 700
OL,17,Ftonnes of cardboard.
OL,26,@qD@bO]
