PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782236889
OL,3,CMajor incident declared after
OL,4,Cexplosions heard and smoke plumes seen
OL,5,Cfor miles
OL,7,F"The whole area here smelled of
OL,8,Fchemicals and it was hard to breathe.
OL,9,FI had a passenger and I left."
OL,11,FPolice have asked motorists to avoid
OL,12,Fthe area and urged people not to
OL,13,Fcongregate at the scene over fears it
OL,14,Fcould hamper the emergency response.
OL,16,FEight fire engines from Cheshire Fire
OL,17,Fand Rescue Service were initially
OL,18,Fdeployed to the plant just before
OL,19,F4.30pm on Monday 22 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
