PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782236889
OL,3,CMajor incident declared after
OL,4,Cexplosions heard and smoke plumes seen
OL,5,Cfor miles
OL,7,FThe blaze spread rapidly and sent
OL,8,Fheavy plumes of smoke visible from as
OL,9,Ffar as the Liverpool, Lytham in
OL,10,FLancashire, north Wales and
OL,11,FMacclesfield in Cheshire.
OL,13,FThe fire service said at 5.30pm that
OL,14,Fthe building was at risk of
OL,15,Fcollapsing, with nearby residents and
OL,16,Fbusinesses urged to keep their windows
OL,17,Fand doors closed.
OL,19,FNo-one is thought to have been injured.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
