PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782236889
OL,3,CMajor incident declared after
OL,4,Cexplosions heard and smoke plumes seen
OL,5,Cfor miles
OL,7,FMotorists are being advised to avoid
OL,8,Fthe area. A number of road closures
OL,9,Fare in place:
OL,11,FCheshire Fire Service later confirmed
OL,12,F20 of its fire engines had been
OL,13,Fdrafted in, with support from crews
OL,14,Ffrom Lancashire and Greater Manchester.
OL,16,FIt was declared a major incident at
OL,17,F6pm as fire fighters continued to
OL,18,Ftackle the blaze.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
