PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782236889
OL,3,CMajor incident declared after
OL,4,Cexplosions heard and smoke plumes seen
OL,5,Cfor miles
OL,7,FFirefighters later said they were
OL,8,Fmaking good progress in tackling the
OL,9,Ffire and preventing it spreading to
OL,10,Fadjacent premises. The smoke plume
OL,11,Fappears to be reducing as a result,
OL,12,Fthey said.
OL,14,FCrews are working in three sectors to
OL,15,Fextinguish the fire systematically
OL,16,Fwith relief crews arriving to continue
OL,17,Fworking into the night.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
