PN,36607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782236889
OL,3,CMajor incident declared after
OL,4,Cexplosions heard and smoke plumes seen
OL,5,Cfor miles
OL,7,FSupt Sam Billington from Cheshire
OL,8,FPolice said, "A large number of
OL,9,Fofficers are in attendance at the
OL,10,Fscene to manage road closures and
OL,11,Fprovide reassurance to the community.
OL,13,F"While our colleagues from Cheshire
OL,14,FFire and Rescue Service tackle the
OL,15,Ffire, we would urge residents in the
OL,16,Fnearby area to follow their advice and
OL,17,Fstay indoors with their windows and
OL,18,Fdoors closed at this time.
